FBIS4-58206 "drnes085_a_94006" FBIS-NES-94-085 Daily Report 2 May 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Armed Men Set Fire To Four Buses in Algiers Armed Men Set Fire To Four Buses in Algiers LD0305083694 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 GMT 2 May 94 LD0305083694 Algiers ENTV Television Network Arabic BFN [Text] Regarding recent terrorist acts, four buses were set on fire this morning at 0400 by an armed group in the center of the capital. The operation took place on the road linking Bouzareah and Bab El Oued when the armed men forced the drivers out and set the buses on fire. This act cost the Urban Transport Company in the capital the loss of about 1 billion centimes.
